      "The big Douglas twenty-one passenger sky\ngiants built and super powered to North-\nwest Airlines' specifications can carry two\nand\nthree-quarters tons of cargo and\npassengers at a speed of 225 miles an\nhour. These smooth, luxurious airliners\nare operated from Chicago to Seattle and\nPortland daily.\n2\nPOST CARD\nPlease address\nand return to\nstewardess whc\nwill stamp and\nmail card\nfor you."
